description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10012578

Atelier Resleriana: The Red Alchemist & the White Guardian is coming to PlayStation®5* on September 26th 2025. 

In Atelier Resleriana: The Red Alchemist & the White Guardian, players follow Rias Eidreise and Slade Clauslyter as they explore mysterious ruins near their hometown, Hallfein. Upon discovering these ruins, Slade’s Geist Core reacts, opening a passage to an alchemist’s atelier filled with secrets that the two protagonists will attempt to unravel. After discovering that the power of Slade’s Geist Core can open gateways to new dimensions, known as the Dimensional Paths, Rias and Slade find a pedestal with strange text written in an unknown language that must be deciphered in order to uncover the secrets of the atelier and restore Hallfein.

#ps5 #ps5games #atelierresleriana
title: Atelier Resleriana: The Red Alchemist & the White Guardian - Story Trailer | PS5 Games

author: PlayStation
description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/street-fighter-6/

The guild authorizes a special collaboration between Street Fighter 6 and Monster Hunter Wilds, the latest installments in both of these iconic franchises!

All players who log in during the event period will get special collab items! The Shop will also be stocked with special EX colors for Blanka, Akuma, Manon, Cammy, and Ken inspired by some wild creatures.

During this event, the Battle Hub will also get a new makeover while we run a special Street Voter event. Finally, the Monster Hunter 20th Anniversary Fighting Pass will return for the collab!

Be sure to stop by and enjoy the festivities while you can!

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games #StreetFighter6 #SF6 #MHWilds #Capcom
title: Street Fighter 6 x Monster Hunter Wilds - Collab Event Announcement Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
